g_item_descs[19769]="^ffffffRequisite Class: ^96f5ffBlademaster^ffffff␀␀␀Requisite Cultivation: ^96f5ffAware of Vacuity^ffffff\rRequisite Skill: ^96f5ffNone^ffffff\rRequisite level: ^96f5ff79\r\r^f7dfa5For 30 seconds, decrease damage you deal by 50% while increasing your critical rate by 25%. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\rRequires one Spark to cast.";
