g_item_descs[25328]="^ffd200The belt has been eaten.\r^ffd200This button can be made into an emblem for memorial.";
g_item_descs[25329]="^ffd200True heroes don't fear long marches!";
g_item_descs[2535]="^ffcb4aQuest: No Ambition\rExcellent wine. The name comes from its osmanthus-like fragrance.";
g_item_descs[2538]="^ffcb4aQuest: No Ambition\rLetter to the wife of Han the Drunkard.";
g_item_descs[2539]="^ffcb4aQuest: No Ambition\rThe wife's reply.";
g_item_descs[25437]="^ffd200Only Kwok Nirvana can identify this book.";
g_item_descs[25438]="^ffcb4aAn order for heroes!\rAll members of a squad can be led into the Valley of Reciprocity  \rby the squad leader with this item, and take battles at Messenger: Wood.\r^00ffffNo level requisition for squad leader.\rAll member must be LV30-55 to enter.";
g_item_descs[25439]="^ffcb4aAn order for heroes!\rAll members of a squad can be led into the Valley of Reciprocity  \rby the squad leader with this item, and take battles at Messenger: Fire.\r^00ffffNo level requisition for squad leader.\rAll member must be LV55-70 to enter.";
g_item_descs[25442]="^ffcb4aQuest: Missing Home\rApothecary Trison's long lost package of nostalgia.\rContains his personal belongings. ";
g_item_descs[25464]="^ffcb4aA young dragon that has not yet learned to fly.\rAt least it can run as fast as the adult ones.\r^00ffffHatch at a Pet Manager.";
g_item_descs[25540]="^ffcb4aA badge found on the body of Lucius. It might be needed in the future.\rBetter keep it for now.\r^ffcb4a'The soul trembles in the depths of the mountain.'";
g_item_descs[25636]="^ffcb4aQuest: Send the Pledge Back\rA letter found on the body of the guard, written in blood. The letter reads: ^808080\r'We were ambushed by those vile fiends. Being outnumbered, I only managed to kill a few of them before\rfalling, but my death does not have to be in vain. The General's Leadership Insignia has been secured.\rShould anyone find it, please deliver it back to General Chugunov.\rMy final thanks goes to you.'";
g_item_descs[25645]="^ffd200The autumn wind is clear, the harvest moon is bright.\rPounding the anvil through the din and the smoke,\rthe autumn is far less pleasant.";
g_item_descs[25647]="^ffd200Shade from a flock of great white geese,\rbeautiful scenery,\rred grass and white leaves.";
g_item_descs[25649]="^ffd200The heartless ones do not suffer the pain of affection,\rwhen an inch can be a thousand miles,\rthe horizon is an eternity away,\rand lovesickness is inexhaustible.";
g_item_descs[25651]="^ffd200Venus frees the poet's soul,\rHades reflects on sudden intimacy.\rThe emperor sleeps\ras his body grows old.";
g_item_descs[25653]="^ffd200The unicorn is plundered,\rthe alarm gong has been rung,\rthe imposing king has been toppled.\rA hero will save us.";
g_item_descs[25655]="^ffd200Climb the highest mountain and gaze out at the sea.\rSwing with all your anger at the unyielding metal.";
g_item_descs[25657]="^ffd200The wind and snow freeze the world outside,\rand the fire and wine keep us warm.\rThe fishing boats are caught by the rain,\rsent to rest on the riverbed.";
g_item_descs[25659]="^ffd200The north wind blows south for thousands of miles.\rEven the flock of geese knows not their own numbers.\rThrough the anger of the skies,\rthey are exhausted when they at last arrive.";
g_item_descs[25661]="^ffd200The clouds are soft.\rSwaying back and forth\rThey reside in the mountains.\rWaiting to comfort travelers.";
g_item_descs[25663]="^ffd200Failure is only a detour; not the end.";
g_item_descs[25665]="^ffd200From error to error\rone discovers the truth.";
g_item_descs[25666]="^ffcb4aSupply Stash reward.\r^00ffff\rAvailable for one week.";
g_item_descs[25668]="^ffd200A promise given was a necessity of the past;\ra promise broken is a necessity of the present.";
g_item_descs[25670]="^ffd200Where there's a will, there's a way.";
g_item_descs[25672]="^ffd200An eye for an eye blinds the world.";
g_item_descs[25674]="^ffd200You fail every risk you do not take.";
g_item_descs[25676]="^ffd200Absence of alternatives clears the mind.";
g_item_descs[25678]="^ffd200Sadness flies away on the wings of time.";
g_item_descs[25680]="^ffd200The more wary you are of danger,\rthe more likely you are to meet it.";
g_item_descs[25682]="^ffd200You've got to do what?\rYou've got to believe!";
g_item_descs[25722]="^ffd200A token rewarded for finishing a challenge from the Tideborn Coming of Age ceremony.\rTurn them in to the Elder of the City of Raging Tides when you have all 7 Tokens.";
g_item_descs[25723]="^ffd200Flowers for those who have sacrificed their lives for their race.";
g_item_descs[25724]="^ffd200Right-click to teleport to Dreamweaver Port.";
g_item_descs[25725]="^ffd200A special net for catching the Staunch Worm on the white beach.\rTarget a worm, and click on this net to catch it.\rThe net has a short duration, so please hurry up.";
