g_item_descs[25820]="^ffd200A rare crystal found in the Palace of Nirvana used to form powerful weapons.\rUse at the Nirvana Forges near the entrance to Palace of Nirvana.";
g_item_descs[25821]="^ffd200A rare crystal found in the Palace of Nirvana used to form powerful armor.\rUse at the Nirvana Armor Forges near the entrance to Palace of Nirvana.";
g_item_descs[25910]="^ffd200A depleted power crystal.";
g_item_descs[25948]="^ffd200Nature does not hurry,\ryet it has accomplished everything.";
g_item_descs[25950]="^ffd200Power is the ultimate aphrodisiac.";
g_item_descs[25952]="^ffd200Songs for the heartbroken can lead to madness.";
g_item_descs[25954]="^ffd200Fear leads to anger.";
g_item_descs[25956]="^ffd200Anger leads to hate.";
g_item_descs[25958]="^ffd200Hate leads to suffering.";
g_item_descs[25960]="^ffd200It is a mistake to look too far ahead.\rOnly one link in the chain of\rdestiny can be handled at a time.";
g_item_descs[25962]="^ffd200One cannot be too careful in the choice of his enemies.";
g_item_descs[25964]="^ffd200The lonely one offers his hand too quickly to whomever he encounters.";
g_item_descs[25966]="^ffd200Love your enemies; they bring out the best in you.";
g_item_descs[25968]="^ffd200If you are strong, your strength will speak for itself.\rIf you are weak, words will be no help.";
g_item_descs[25970]="^ffd200To try your best is to be destined to fail.";
g_item_descs[25972]="^ffd200Without courage, all other virtues lose their meaning.";
g_item_descs[25974]="^ffd200Let go of who you are,\rand become what you might be.";
g_item_descs[25976]="^ffd200Being loved by someone gives you strength,\rwhile loving someone gives you courage.";
g_item_descs[25978]="^ffd200One who wastes an hour of life,\rhas not discovered its value.";
g_item_descs[25980]="^ffd200The grass must bend when the wind blows across it.";
g_item_descs[25982]="^ffd200Help yourself, and heavens will help you.";
g_item_descs[25984]="^ffd200The problem with the Wraithgate... is that it's full of Wraiths!";
g_item_descs[25985]="^ffd200A pair of beads left by the Tideborn Traitor. Two names are carved on the beads, indicating that they could be her token of love.\rThough she was a traitor, have some compassion and take the beads to the waters of White Sand Beach.";
g_item_descs[26046]="^ffcb4aQuest: Missing Captain\rAn antique that looks very old. It would be best to give it to Merchant Ambassador Shimmin.";
g_item_descs[26047]="^ffcb4aQuest: Soul of the Scarecrow\rA crystal harvested from a possessed scarecrow. Bring it back to the Elder.";
g_item_descs[26049]="^ffcb4aLegend speaks of a hitman who disguised himself as a cook and hid a dagger in a fish dinner. \rAs he served the dinner to his victim, he pulled out the dagger \rand successfully stabbed his target to death. ";
g_item_descs[26050]="^ffcb4aThe hero of the immortal legend!\r^00ffffRank equipment. Cannot be decomposed.";
g_item_descs[26053]="^ffcb4aWe choose our joys and sorrows\rlong before we experience them.";
g_item_descs[26054]="^ffd200Patience and passage of time\rdo more than strength and fury.";
g_item_descs[26057]="^ffcb4aYou cannot run from death. Sooner or later, you'll run into death.\rThis weapon bears death's name upon it,\rbringing death to you.";
g_item_descs[26058]="^ffcb4aThe hero of the immortal legend!\r^00ffffRank equipment. Cannot be decomposed.";
g_item_descs[26061]="^ffcb4aPoets are only the interpreters of the gods.";
g_item_descs[26062]="^ffd200Sometimes, a sword is just a sword.";
