g_item_descs[27424]="^aaaaaaBoosts your efficiency of leveling.\r^ffcb4aTo Activate:\r^00ffffChoose 'Hyper EXP' in the Public Relations menu.\rChoose the desired Hyper EXP session and select 'Confirm'.\r^ffcb4aHyper EXP has 3 Stages:\r^00ffffHyper EXP - Multiply EXP/Spirit gains according to session selected.\rBuffer Time - The period of normal EXP/Spirit gain.\rExhaustion - The period of reduced EXP gains (EXP/Spirit gain reduced by 90%).\rBuffer Time will begin when Hyper EXP wears off.\rExhaustion will begin when Buffer Time wears off, or the player is logged off.\r^ffcb4aHyper EXP can be combined with other EXP and Spirit gaining effects (Training Esoterica).";
